	<conbody>
		<section id="content_inventory_term">
			<p>A content inventory is an inventory of documents (DITA and non-DITA) in an existing document set.</p>
			<p>The inventory is input to a documentation plan involving changes to the existing documents, new use of related documents, or the creation of new documents.</p>
		</section>
